    "summary": "Accomplished executive with over 15 years experiences in international strategic management, international business development, sales/ key account and general business sustainability management. As a result-oriented, driven and a decisive leader with proven success in international business development, I had the opportunity to learn not only  the resilience, tenacity and the agility in achieving business results and strategic positioning in markets but also the conviction in leading teams and enhancing the growth in organisations.\n\nTrack record of providing strategic direction on bilateral economic activities as well as sustainable investment and trade in international business environment. Providing direction and overseeing business operations including people management, developing new portfolios and growing the bottom-line in a consistent manner whilst reducing costs.\n\nIn the leadership landscape and through strategic leadership for international stakeholder management and sustainability strategy development (integration of SDGs, circular business models & circular economy), I have always considered the design, development and execution of strategies that enables a powerful shared value to fit not only with the prosperity purpose of today but also with a brighter future for people and our only one planet. \n\nExcel in dynamic, demanding and international environments while extensive traveling is part of my function, I remain focused, passionate, positive, pragmatic and determined to be part of a sustainable solution!\n\n+International business development.\n+Growth strategy.\n+Strategic leadership.\n+International alliances.\n+Strategic market positioning.\n+Territory growth management.\n+VUCA strategic management.\n+Tactical high-stake negotiations.\n+Sales management. \n+Sales strategy development.\n+Customer success and acquisition.\n+Budget/ sales forecasting.\n+Revenue generation.\n+Commercial excellence.\n+Channel establishment.\n+Team coaching & mentoring.\n+People management.\n+Problem solving. \n+business acumen.\n+Extensive traveling.\n+Partnership management.\n+Public speaking and presentation.\n",
